bers in a crowdfunding-style fundraiser that not only contributes to our organization and scholars, but also offers the opportunity to bring your social circle and\/or family in a socially-conscious activity.<\/p><\/li>\t<\/ul>\n\t<h3>How To Give<\/h3>\n\t<h5>Choose to give your donation via credit or debit card, Electronic Funds Transfer (EFT), cash, or check.<\/h5>\n\t<h6><strong>For check donations, please mail to:<\/strong><\/h6>\n<h6>Islamic Scholarship Fund<br \/>\n1935 Addison St Suite A<br \/>\nBerkeley, CA 94704<\/h6>\n<h6>For wire donations, please email us at <strong><a href=\"mailto:Contact@IslamicScholarshipFund.org\">Contact@IslamicScholarshipFund.org<\/a><\/strong>. To give via credit or debit card, or an EFT, visit our secure <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/secure.islamicscholarshipfund.org\/np\/clients\/islamicscholarshipfund\/donation.jsp?test=true&amp;campaign=29&amp;\">Online Donation Form<\/a><\/strong>.<\/h6>\n\t<h3>More Ways to Give<\/h3>\n\t<h4>Join ISF&#8217;s Sustainers Circle<\/h4>\n\t<p>Our Sustainers Circle offers an exclusive opportunity for our most esteemed supporters to invest in the long-term stability of our Cycle of Support\u00a0through a\u00a0<em>Waqf<\/em>, or religious endowment.\u00a0Establishing an endowment ensures that your values and priorities as a donor are maintained by our organization for perpetuity.<\/p>\n\t\t\t<a href=\"https:\/\/islamicscholarshipfund.org\/sustainers-circle\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tLearn More \n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/islamicscholarshipfund.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/Rami-Koujah.-Law-scaled-1.jpg\" alt=\"Rami Koujah. Law\" itemprop=\"image\" height=\"2557\" width=\"2560\" title=\"Rami Koujah. Law\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"  \/>\n\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/islamicscholarshipfund.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/Nesima.jpg\" alt=\"Nesima\" itemprop=\"image\" height=\"640\" width=\"960\" title=\"Nesima\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"  \/>\n\t<h4>Donate Stock or Mutual Funds<\/h4>\n\t<p>Donating stock and mutual fund shares is an effective way to help ISF support the next generation of American Muslim leaders. Making this gift is simple and offers you valuable financial benefits:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>You can donate appreciated stocks, bonds, or mutual funds.<\/li>\n<li>The total value of the stock upon transfer is tax-deductible.<\/li>\n<li>There is no obligation to pay any capital gains taxes on the appreciation.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\t\t\t<a href=\"https:\/\/islamicscholarshipfund.org\/stock-donations\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tLearn More \n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t<h4>Donate Your Car<\/h4>\n\t<p>Have an old car you could donate? Through our partnership with Cars4Jannah, you can support ISF without donating cash. Becoming a partner is free and scheduling car pickup is quick and easy. You will also receive a tax receipt for your donation.<\/p>\n\t\t\t<a href=\"https:\/\/cars4jannah.com\/IslamicScholarshipFund\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tLearn More \n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/islamicscholarshipfund.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/Screen-Shot-2021-03-03-at-3.56.53-PM.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-03-03 at 3.56.53 PM\" itemprop=\"image\" height=\"956\" width=\"954\" title=\"Screen Shot 2021-03-03 at 3.56.53 PM\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"  \/>\n\t <iframe src=\"https:\/\/doublethedonation.com\/api\/integrations\/neoncrm-plugin-iframe\/sOKqhHDT8R9x2cLp\"> <\/iframe> \n\t<h4>Matching Gifts<\/h4>\n\t<p>Does your place of business match charitable donations? Many companies or organizations offer this program as a way to double the impact of your gift. ISF works with Double the Donation to make the process simple and easy. Search your company name in the form to the left, and Double the Donation will take it from there.<\/p>\n\t<h3>How Your Donation Is Used<\/h3>\